# VEHICLE::SET_AIRCRAFT_IGNORE_HIGHTMAP_OPTIMISATION

## Summary
Sets the aircraft to ignore an optimistation that checks the height map before doing wheel probes

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **BOOL** ignoreHeightMap
